      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IVORY HAMADA (4) has a strong record here with four wins and three placings from 10 starts. Missed the frame latest (22.24) when fifth over 390m at this track in a Grade 4/5. Has the ability and should feature. ASTON SASHA (2) stalked the lead and fought on well to finish 5 lengths away in second (25.84) at Warrnambool in a Grade 5 over 450m. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Well-placed to take this out. SCOTT EPHRAIM (3) was below best last time when fifth but prior to that was a Rank Limit - Grade 5 winner in quick time at this track. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. PAW PASCAL (7) can find the frame without surprising.",
